OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service introduces
OL,4,Cchanges to how it responds to strokes
OL,6,FUnder the new orange category, people
OL,7,Fwould undergo "rapid clinical
OL,8,Fscreening" by nurses and paramedics in
OL,9,Fcall centres to help identify the
OL,10,Fpatients requiring the most time
OL,11,Fsensitive care.
OL,13,FThe change follows an announcement on
OL,14,FJuly 1, which created new categories
OL,15,Ffor cardiac and respiratory arrest and
OL,16,Flife-threatening emergencies.
