OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service introduces
OL,4,Cchanges to how it responds to strokes
OL,6,FAnnouncing the changes, Health
OL,7,FSecretary Jeremy Miles said they would
OL,8,F"help ensure that people experiencing
OL,9,Fa stroke receive the rapid, tailored
OL,10,Fresponse they need to survive, recover
OL,11,Fand thrive following a stroke."
OL,13,FThe new categories, which replace the
OL,14,Fcurrent amber category, are scheduled
OL,15,Fto be implemented before winter this
OL,16,Fyear as part of a new emergency
OL,17,Fambulance performance framework,
OL,18,Faccording to the Welsh Government.
OL,20,FThe changes replace the current
OL,21,Fcategories with:
