OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service introduces
OL,4,Cchanges to how it responds to strokes
OL,6,FAs well as a change to the
OL,7,Fcategorisation of 999 calls, a pre-
OL,8,Fhospital Video Triage approach is
OL,9,Fbeing piloted at five Welsh stroke
OL,10,Fservices with support of the ambulance
OL,11,Fservice.
OL,13,FThis sees real time communication
OL,14,Fbetween pre-hospital clinicians, such
OL,15,Fas ambulance clinicians, and hospital
OL,16,Fstroke specialists, to improve the
OL,17,Fassessment and diagnosis of stroke.
