OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service introduces
OL,4,Cchanges to how it responds to strokes
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government says early
OL,7,Ffindings show it supports clinical
OL,8,Fdecision making and improves pre-
OL,9,Farrival information for hospital
OL,10,Fteams, speeding up access to life
OL,11,Fsaving and life changing treatments.
OL,13,FHealth Secretary Jeremy Miles said:
OL,14,F"For people in stroke, every minute
OL,15,Fcounts if lives are to be saved and
OL,16,Fdisability reduced or prevented - with
OL,17,Feach minute that passes, around two
OL,18,Fmillion brain cells are lost.
