OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service introduces
OL,4,Cchanges to how it responds to strokes
OL,6,F"That's why we're introducing a new
OL,7,Forange category into the system which
OL,8,Fwill help our ambulance service
OL,9,Fidentify time sensitive complaints
OL,10,Fsuch as stroke quickly and get
OL,11,Fpatients the right specialist
OL,12,Ftreatment faster.
OL,14,F"This will help ensure that people
OL,15,Fexperiencing a stroke receive the
OL,16,Frapid, tailored response they need to
OL,17,Fsurvive, recover and thrive following
OL,18,Fa stroke."
