OL,3,CWelsh Ambulance Service introduces
OL,4,Cchanges to how it responds to strokes
OL,6,FAndy Swinburn, Executive Director of
OL,7,FParamedicine at the Welsh Ambulance
OL,8,FService, said they welcome the changes.
OL,10,F"The nature of how patients present to
OL,11,F999 has changed and it's important to
OL,12,Freflect this in the way we respond,
OL,13,Ffirst and foremost to increase
OL,14,Fambulance availability for those who
OL,15,Ftruly need it but also to ensure that
OL,16,Fpatients who can be cared for closer
OL,17,Fto home get that opportunity.
